{"tid":1364336,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101(2)條: 公民拘捕權","createTime":"2019-07-25T10:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:42:20.000Z","uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff5af0561ce72242e4eb037d0723962ddc8d02c","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"就咁既，如果見到有人比人打，你可以行使「公民拘捕權」去制服佢，成個個程最重要係有人拍片，有人做人證，有人出手制服施襲者，所以最好唔好走散，大約29人為一個單位，但如果你真係唔夠人手咁點呀？Call 消防囉 Call救護囉！<br />\n<br />\n自己香港自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n////&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;////<br />\n<br />\n《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101(2)條︰「任何人可無需手令而逮捕任何他『合理地懷疑』犯了『可逮捕的罪行』的人。」<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n<br />\n（一）只適用於「可逮捕的罪行」<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，「可逮捕的罪行」是指可判處超過12個月監禁的罪行，但陸偉雄指在牆上貼便條、撕下他人的便條、互相推撞等均不屬此列，襲擊、傷人、謀殺、縱火等則屬可逮捕的罪行，「但一般市民有機會錯誤判斷」，一旦誤用有機會構成「非法禁錮」等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n（二）誤傷疑犯可反被指控<br />\n<br />\n陸偉雄提醒，市民制服疑犯時只可使用合理武力，包括不可故意傷害疑犯，然而疑犯有可能奮力反抗掙扎，即使使用合理武力，過程中仍有機會誤傷疑犯，令其扭傷手、骨折等，仍然有機會構成「襲擊」等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n（三）拍攝影片須紀錄完整過程<br />\n<br />\n常言道「有片有真相」，惟陸偉雄提醒用作舉證的影片，愈完全紀錄整個衝突過程，愈是有力證據，相反如只拍頭、拍尾，或曾被剪輯、修改均影響其可信性，同時對方亦會對影片真實性提出質疑。"},{"pid":"7d58e183f7d9cc58d531ea31636997acf3ce8abc","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"500d2c42899524f01934c3cd29c11f0cbdf656ef","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"有用野無人推？"},{"pid":"71b2baf42089320f5e7f04b3c658dd3031a2fa34","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:57:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef93eeefc2e81699954a689e128cfbcfa7623159","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ec2f7c869884bcc65c53112238726a1285da43c","tid":1364336,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544e2e07da2f778311691d83f71ba215eea39d10","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ab68b0b7ba4ae89a20952b444186d5065f19d0f","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8b6f0900e912420dbd5541c29301194d10c5f39","tid":1364336,"uid":106697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"捱"},{"pid":"cca292e709290c3614544cc9b98f496fd218c253","tid":1364336,"uid":106697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8b6f0900e912420dbd5541c29301194d10c5f39","tid":1364336,"uid":106697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"捱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80700038f4c38f82996037a4c6b11eab9d67906c","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d755bb6a7963b8aaf2662d88ca3f17a130e63b3","tid":1364336,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"好重要"}]}